{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.04","c":"أَلَمْ","d":"alam","e":"ْmَlَaʾ"},{"b":"0.57","h":"0.77","c":"تَرَ","d":"tara","e":"َrَt"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.48","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"kayfa","e":"َfْyَk"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.57","c":"فَعَلَ","d":"faʿala","e":"َlَʿعَf"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.63","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"َkُّbَr"},{"b":"3.2","h":"5.14","c":"بِأَصْحَابِ","d":"bi-aṣḥābi","e":"ِbَٰḥْṣَaʾِb"},{"b":"4.5","h":"7.32","c":"الْفِيلِ","d":"l-fīli","e":"ِlyِfْlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"Have you not considered, [O Muhammad], how your Lord dealt with the companions of the elephant?","ihya":"<div class='ihya-container' style='margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #d4af37; border-radius: 4px;'><h4 style='color: #d4af37; margin-bottom: 15px; font-family: \"Cinzel\", serif;'>Ihya 'Ulum al-Din Commentary</h4><div class='ihya-entry'><span class='badge badge-light' style='color: #666; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin-bottom: 8px;'>Vol4 book6</span><div class='ihya-text' style='font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;'>Indeed, at times He makes Himself known to them through His acts that inspire fear [khawf] and hope [raja'], and He recites to them His established way [sunnah] concerning His enemies and His prophets, saying: \"Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with the companions of the elephant [ashab al-fil]?\"</div></div></div>"}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.15","h":"0.4","c":"أَلَمْ","d":"alam","e":"ْmَlَaʾ"},{"b":"0.62","h":"1.12","c":"يَجْعَلْ","d":"yajʿal","e":"ْlَʿعْjgَy"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.46","c":"كَيْدَهُمْ","d":"kaydahum","e":"ْmُhَdْyَk"},{"b":"2.5","h":"4.25","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"àِf"},{"b":"2.9","h":"5","c":"تَضْلِيلٍ","d":"taḍlīlin","e":"ٍlyِlْḍَt"}],"a":{"g":"Did He not make their plan into misguidance?"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.3","c":"وَأَرْسَلَ","d":"wa-arsala","e":"َlَsْrَaʾَw"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.66","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"ْmِhْyَlَʿع"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.65","c":"طَيْرًا","d":"ṭayran","e":"āًrْyَṭ"},{"b":"2.9","h":"5.38","c":"أَبَابِيلَ","d":"abābīla","e":"َlyِbāَbَaʾ"}],"a":{"g":"And He sent against them birds in flocks,"}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.1","c":"تَرْمِيهِمْ","d":"tarmīhim","e":"mِhyِmْrَt"},{"b":"2.0","h":"2.42","c":"بِحِجَارَةٍ","d":"biḥijāratin","e":"ٍẗَrāَjgِḥِb"},{"b":"4.6","h":"5.47","c":"مِنْ","d":"min","e":"nِّm"},{"b":"5.6","h":"6.36","c":"سِجِّيلٍ","d":"sijjīlin","e":"ٍlyِّjgِs"}],"a":{"g":"Striking them with stones of hard clay,"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"فَجَعَلَهُمْ","d":"fajaʿalahum","e":"ْmُhَlَʿعَjgَf"},{"b":"1.2","h":"1.92","c":"كَعَصْفٍ","d":"kaʿaṣfin","e":"ٍfْṣَʿعَk"},{"b":"3.5","h":"4.57","c":"مَأْكُولٍ","d":"makūlin","e":"ٍۭlwُkْaʾَّm"}],"a":{"g":"And He made them like eaten straw."}}}